comment: Durant (OKC) and James (CLE) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
Thompson (CLE) and Singler (OKC) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of a 24 Second Violation was confirmed.
Ibaka (OKC) sets the screen on Jefferson (CLE) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
As Ibaka (OKC) cuts, James (CLE) switches with Thompson (CLE) and Ibaka and James make incidental contact with one another.
Jefferson (CLE) and Durant (OKC) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
After both players get their hands on the ball, Westbrook (OKC) and Thompson (CLE) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Jefferson (CLE) and Durant (OKC) briefly engage and separate during the inbounds play.
Thompson (CLE) and Ibaka (OKC) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Adams (OKC) commits a take foul on James (CLE).
